                <note rend="inline" type="source">867n.404Wailing Wall/24: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul General at Jerusalem</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Knabenshue</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-08-24T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 24, 1929—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your August 23, 6 p.m. Keep Department informed by telegraph. Department presumes
                    that no injury has been done to American citizens or their property.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Carr</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
